{"tid":1816273,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"【中美大戰】中原施永青：樓價今年將跌5%至10%  VS 美聯黃建業： 料今年樓價升5%","createTime":"2020-01-08T06:23:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-12T16:16:21.000Z","uid":79563,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"effebb8c12d417ba8321ee58f3e4a21948e03c23","tid":1816273,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T06:23:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1501638_1_L_20200108135151.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1501638_1_L_20200108135151.jpg&h=085f836c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中原集團主席施永青出席論壇後表示，雖然社會平靜或帶動內部消費改善，但香港及全球增長動力減慢，就業及工資加幅受到影響，樓市的利淡因素較多，料今年樓價將跌5-10%。<br />\n<br />\n他指，部分新盤銷情造好可能與單位較小或價錢吸引有關，貨尾單位的消化速度仍然不高，可能要到農曆年之後才會出現小陽春，購買力重新釋放。<br />\n<br />\n施永青又說，現時樓價跌幅較小，政府可能要到樓價明顯回調，而且預期措施不會刺激樓市明顯反彈，才會考慮放寬樓市辣招，認為政府可先考慮撤銷短期額外印花稅。<br />\n<br />\n另外，他提到，現時中原未有裁員或縮舖計劃。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/cis/5e12ef5dfd5cc31c9c2b92d0.jpg/OonRFvHmiq-tFhtm1sKofFYi9UzmYGUPSZ9jYEmfY2A?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fcis%2F5e12ef5dfd5cc31c9c2b92d0.jpg%2FOonRFvHmiq-tFhtm1sKofFYi9UzmYGUPSZ9jYEmfY2A%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=897e67b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n反修例示威活動持續已經超過半年，加上中美貿易戰影響，去年經濟增長放緩，樓價亦見回軟。不過美聯集團（1200）主席黃建業估計，今年樓價會呈「U型」，先跌後升最多5%。"},{"pid":"53e3a4ee2580c761a81949ea44bffddbc27326ef","tid":1816273,"uid":4575,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T06:24:38.000Z","msg":"我係中原買美聯放，今次fatfat啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce43cd42c69619525b23c8ca59d7b42fec2c2cf7","tid":1816273,"uid":40979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T06:31:08.000Z","msg":"只信汪總"},{"pid":"4034ce37358024e9fe1cca9cf4a653b09dee8161","tid":1816273,"uid":236646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T07:00:44.000Z","msg":"中原居然會睇淡"},{"pid":"1207909a085788e9685bda65849661f4bb4b94a0","tid":1816273,"uid":236646,"like":3,"dislike":6,"score":-3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T07:08:06.000Z","msg":"施生似鳩UP多, 趺到10% 真係好難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n5%已經好多人搶住買"},{"pid":"a8680b53083e8c510462f14c334ff6ec9bc422a8","tid":1816273,"uid":3358,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"1207909a085788e9685bda65849661f4bb4b94a0","tid":1816273,"uid":236646,"like":3,"dislike":6,"score":-3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T07:08:06.000Z","msg":"施生似鳩UP多, 趺到10% 真係好難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n5%已經好多人搶住買"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T07:17:43.000Z","msg":"經濟環境轉差<br />\nD人驚份工保唔住就算跌5%都唔會急入市了"},{"pid":"1a804c455906a69585131a597a52e56621acec4e","tid":1816273,"uid":89861,"like":8,"dislike":4,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"1207909a085788e9685bda65849661f4bb4b94a0","tid":1816273,"uid":236646,"like":3,"dislike":6,"score":-3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T07:08:06.000Z","msg":"施生似鳩UP多, 趺到10% 真係好難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n5%已經好多人搶住買"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T07:19:54.000Z","msg":"97 個時個個都咁諗"},{"pid":"c093692f6dbc6daf47abb7fd6e62e4bfe86baab1","tid":1816273,"uid":125688,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ce43cd42c69619525b23c8ca59d7b42fec2c2cf7","tid":1816273,"uid":40979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T06:31:08.000Z","msg":"只信汪總"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T10:36:38.000Z","msg":"2018年話一年後嘉湖三房不低於650萬？"},{"pid":"06482d8deb